		||	PCM_FDC_DRV1_MFS16
	prompt "DD/DS-80T 5*1024 0ST (800k, CPA)"
	---help---
		800/800/794kB CPA format:

		  - 2 sides per disk (DS)
		  - 80 tracks per side (DD)
		  - 5 sectors per track
		  - 1024 byte per sector
		  - 2048 byte BDOS block size
		  - no system tracks
		  - 192 directory entries (6kB)

